text:
Name: Donna Ritter.
Graduation Year: 2022.
Description: Donna Ritter is a dedicated Sociology student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in sociology research and practical applications. They aspire to become a lawyer advocating for human rights and justice. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
